Underrated admirable character: Mark from the Jason Genova saga videos. Had an insanely tough life, nightmarish health issues in his teens, multiple surgeries, had to take care of his sick parents for years and almost offed himself from depression. Still benched 4 plates for reps

Reason he was always doing close grip bench upper body stuff is he was physically unable to squat after being bedridden for years and having his glues surgically removed down to the bone. He was taking care of his dying father during most of the vids. Never took it out on anyone.
